		"References": "<strong>Final rule implementing Amendment 78:</strong></br><a href=\"http://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/FR-2006-06-28/pdf/06-5761.pdf\">http://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/FR-2006-06-28/pdf/06-5761.pdf</a></br><strong>Final rule implementing clarification of closed area boundaries:</strong></br><a href=\"http://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/FR-2007-11-09/pdf/E7-22050.pdf\">http://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/FR-2007-11-09/pdf/E7-22050.pdf</a></br><strong>Final rule implementing Amendment 88:</strong></br><a href=\"http://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/FR-2008-02-19/html/08-707.htm\">http://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/FR-2008-02-19/html/08-707.htm</a></br><strong>Aleutian Islands Fishery Ecosystem Plan:</strong></br><a href=\"http://www.npfmc.org/wp-content/PDFdocuments/conservation_issues/AIFEP/AIFEP12_07.pdf\">http://www.npfmc.org/wp-content/PDFdocuments/conservation_issues/AIFEP/AIFEP12_07.pdf</a></br><strong>Essential Fish Habitat Consultation Guidance:</strong></br><a href=\"http://www.habitat.noaa.gov/pdf/efh_consultation_guidance_v1_1.pdf\">http://www.habitat.noaa.gov/pdf/efh_consultation_guidance_v1_1.pdf</a></br><strong>Proposed rule on EFH and HAPC areas:</strong> </br><a href=\"https://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/FR-2006-02-06/html/06-1083.htm\">https://www.gpo.gov/fdsys/pkg/FR-2006-02-06/html/06-1083.htm</a>"
